twitch_info.title: Kamilia III - Nue
twitch_info.description:
Just over 7 hours. P6 was incredibly hard (but fun), and P8 was pretty tricky too. Learning the pattern was a challenge but didn't take as long as I thought it would, and the rest of the fight honestly didn't seem that bad. My opinion would probably change if I died on the final two attacks, which...came kinda close.
All secret bosses down!
